Android application for monitoring the price of bitcoins on the now defunct [[Mt. Gox|MtGox]].

[Screen](http://media1.android-apps.com/images/pname/c/com.btc.watcher/image1.png) [snapshots](http://media1.android-apps.com/images/pname/c/com.btc.watcher/image2.png) are available from the April 2nd, 2011 review by Android Apps (1.1).

The application's availability was announced on February 19th, 2011 (1.2).  

